Voltages: 
PPBUS_g3h 8.62V; PP3V42_g3h 3.41V; PP5V_s0 0v; PPVRTC_G3H 3.33V; ALL_SYS_PWRGD 0V; PP5V_S4RS3 0V~ fast pulse; PM_SLP_S4_L 1.46V; PM_SLP_S3_BUF_L pulse and 0V back;
